source.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Light Bulbs
source.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 4.3 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Compact Fluorescent Lamps (CFLs) that are effective as of December 2, 2008 or the Integral LED Lamps Version 1.4 Requirements that are effective as of August 31, 2010. Some data may not be available for products certified before January 1, 2011. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=cfls.pr_crit_cfls or http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=iledl.pr_key_product
